Hi Priyanka,&nbsp; 





I have provided access to support@pluginhive.com&nbsp; 





While you are at it, there are 2 more things that is causing issues.&nbsp; 


 When creating shipment, how can we add note for the carrier? Sometimes customer has left notes on order that we need to pass to the carrier for correct delivery. How do we do this with PluginHive? 

 Default option for delivery instructions like - “Leave in safe place” : We’ve had customers complaining that the carrier took the parcel back as no one answered the door. In most cases we need to tell carrier
 to leave in safe place as a default option. How do we set this in PluginHive? 






Thanks 





Regards, 

Kennedy Wild

